HEADWORD: Fichu
<hw>Fich"u</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.,
neckerchief.]</ety> <def>A light cape, usually of lace, worn by women,
to cover the neck and throat, and extending to the shoulders.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

